Step1:Start

Step2:Read the elements limits 'n'

Step3:Read 'n' elements into an arr[]

Step4:Repeat the following step until i<n-1

    Step4.1:min=i,initaliz j=i+1

    Step4.2:Repeat the following step until j<n 

        Step4.2.1:if arr[j]<arr[min]
                          min=j
    Step4.3:Swap arr[i] $ arr[min]

Step5:Display sorted elements
